Installation :

1. This program uses Laravel v4.2 framework
2. Serve it using apache
3. Your document root must be /public folder 


Database Installation/Configuration :

1. This program uses MySQL as persistent data storage system.
2. A dump is in yumist.sql
3. For configuring connection details edit /app/config/database.php


Documentation for REST APIs :

1. This program uses swagger for generating documentation.
2. Please hit http://localhost/api-docs to get documentation on browser. (Assuming you install it at localhost)


Testing the installation :

1. Point to GET http://localhost/status you must see "Feeling yummy :)" as message

